infrastructure: schools, office blocks, stores and service premises, stylish
cafes and restaurants and city transport. Nearby are tram stops and the nearby Bulwary Wiślane are friendly for walks, bicycle trips and recreation.
The apartment of 43 sqm is composed of:
- a spacious living room with the equipped kitchenette. The apartment is equipped with top quality structures (induction stove, oven, dishwasher, kettle, large fridge) and all necessary household appliances for everyday use.
- a spacious and comfy bedroom with double bed and work space;
- functional wardrobe;
- bathroom fitted with a spacious shower, washing machine, toilet, big mirror and a heater;
- bright hall
The apartment has been finished to high standard in every detail.
An undoubted advantage of the property is its spacious sunny balcony.
The apartment also has a basement (included in the price) where bicycles may be kept.
ADVANTAGES OF THE INVESTMENT:
- prestigious investment "Vistula Apartmets"
- charming district of Cracow - Stare Podgórze, Zabłocie, Kazimierz
- modern building with a noiseless elevator
- municipal heating;
- apartment with no gas system;
- finished comfortably;
- access control;
- railway station PKP Zabłocie nearby;
- close to Bulwary Wiślane and a new bicycle-foot bridge
- Galeria Kazimierz shopping mall on the other side of the Vistula River
